&gt;&lt;br&gt;梦境好像只把欢愉借你片刻&lt;br&gt;可这个夜晚真实的属于你&lt;br&gt;这是一场漫长的重逢&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;我们都捧着真心&lt;br&gt;走了很远的路才到这里&lt;br&gt;一步动摇都会相差千里&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;所以你也不必准备万全再来见面&lt;br&gt;我们欢迎欣喜 同样承接狼狈&lt;br&gt;彼此信任的必要条件&lt;br&gt;是我在这里 我能看见你&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;我们默契开口 唱出同样的旋律&lt;br&gt;短暂的丢掉经历、放掉头脑&lt;br&gt;只释放和面对真实的情绪&lt;br&gt;这正是「追」来的意义———&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;千千万万的路口&lt;br&gt;请你毅然决然奔向自己&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;下一站，「追」向杭州&lt;img a=&quot;2048&quot; b=&quot;3071&quot; style=&quot;a:2048px;b:3071px;&quot; src=&quot;http://10.0.0.22/weibo/images/d08a699e5c8d2ae5f655e701c89b6a07_thumb.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;img a=&quot;2048&quot; b=&quot;1565&quot; style=&quot;a:2048px;b:1565px;&quot; src=&quot;http://10.0.0.22/weibo/images/6702cf8f8c19fce8ccdabc2b9d48bb9c_thumb.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;img a=&quot;2048&quot; b=&quot;2730&quot; style=&quot;a:2048px;b:2730px;&quot; src=&quot;http://10.0.0.22/weibo/images/5ca89c17b8b6d369341bf6e86d8664e5_thumb.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;img a=&quot;2048&quot; b=&quot;2750&quot; style=&quot;a:2048px;b:2750px;&quot; src=&quot;http://10.0.0.22/weibo/images/e48e224d26db18768e35a1ab46d8669b_thumb.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;img a=&quot;2048&quot; b=&quot;2731&quot; style=&quot;a:2048px;b:2731px;&quot; src=&quot;http://10.0.0.22/weibo/images/8f2d7b28528bc81084571f39335be440_thumb.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;img a=&quot;2048&quot; b=&quot;2730&quot; style=&quot;a:2048px;b:2730px;&quot; src=&quot;http://10.0.0.22/weibo/images/7169e56da75617808bbdd0753c167f5f_thumb.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;img a=&quot;2048&quot; b=&quot;2730&quot; style=&quot;a:2048px;b:2730px;&quot; src=&quot;http://10.0.0.22/weibo/images/658be7d41abfe1c20165d2d9a2dcd061_thumb.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;img a=&quot;2048&quot; b=&quot;2730&quot; style=&quot;a:2048px;b:2730px;&quot; src=&quot;ht